{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Identifies and selects the next audible track, reporting its name and peak info. We collect left and right peaks from track meters if playing, or read reapeak cache files for items if project is stopped. Muted tracks aren's aren't included.\par}
}

{\rtf1\ansi\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0 \fswiss Helvetica;}{\f1 \fmodern Courier;}}
{\colortbl;\red255\green0\blue0;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\widowctrl\hyphauto

{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Identifies and selects the previous audible track, reporting its name and peak info. We collect left and right peaks from track meters if playing, or read reapeak cache files for items if project is stopped. Muted tracks aren's aren't included.\par}
}

